Package: prettyping
Version: 1.1.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Denilson Sa <denilsonsa@gmail.com>
Depends: bash, awk
Architecture: all
Description: A wrapper around the standard ping 'tool', making the output prettier, more colorful, 
 more compact, and easier to read.
 The utility prettyping runs the standard ping in the background and parses its output, 
 showing the ping responses in a graphical way at the terminal 
